<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-6895] camel-xmljson: Encoding is not considered while marhaling</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-6895</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The encoding specified in the DataFormat properties should be passed to OutputStreamWriter constructor in XmlJsonDataFormat.marshal method, otherwise it is not being considered.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;OutputStreamWriter osw = new OutputStreamWriter(stream, encoding);&lt;/p&gt;</description>
