                            <comment id="13805236" author="njiang" created="Fri, 25 Oct 2013 11:42:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oh, it&apos;s my fault. The feature that I just added was supposed to change the encoding dynamically (per message)&lt;br/&gt;
